APCs, drones, engineering equipment: Germany provided Ukraine with a new package of military aid. Read more about this on the website of the German government. Yes, the new military package included: ● 18 armored personnel carriers;
● 11 mine trawls;
● DACHS armored engineering vehicle;

● 10 reconnaissance drones Vector (flight range up to 25 km for 2 hours, has vertical takeoff and landing, works around the clock);

● 30 RQ-35 Heidrun reconnaissance drones (flight range up to 30 km);

● 11 Primoco ONE reconnaissance drones (flight range up to 1,500 km at an altitude of up to 3.3 km for 15 hours, payload - up to 30 kg, automated take-off and landing, autonomous flight plan execution);

● 7 Songbird reconnaissance drones.

